v4.0.0

Steps to Install Horizon

1. Install Java JDK 1.8 (Not Built in)
2. Open Computer.
3. Right Click on Computer and Chose Properties
4. Choose Advanced System Settings.
5. Click On Environment Variables
6. Click On Add
7. Type "Path"(Without quotes) as the name
8. In the Value, enter the value to the bin folder of the JavaJDK(Search GOOGLE for more)
9. Click On OK Twice/Thrice
10. Now, Go to GameMaker/out/artifacts/LoginStuff_jar
11. Start LoginStuff
12. Enjoy!

For any support, Choose Issues at the Help Menu of the program

Remember: Horizon Team Will always be there for you.

Thank you for choosing Horizon


